plot: Scott becomes devastated when he hears a rumor about Kourtney; Kim returns to work and fears she might not be cut out from her public life; Kendall gets upset with Caitlyn when her efforts to spend time with her dad are taken for granted.

Scott is devastated when he hears a rumor that Kourtney is hooking up with another guy and spirals back into old vices. After taking some personal time after her robbery in Paris, Kim is back to work and fears she might not be cut out for her public lifestyle anymore. Kendall gets upset with Caitlyn when her efforts to spend time with her dad are taken for granted.
